Let’s not forget football is entertainment and ozil is an entertainer.

Both teams still have a lot of problems and both need to strengthen in january , united need midfielders and a skilfull winger , arsenal need mostly defenders.
Lets hope both teams can be great again in the future and fight for the title again like we did in the past!

snippet.textDisplay:
I have seen the match 4 times today and there are a few key things we must take notice and have patience with:

1)Ozil still has the legs. Though not as much as in their face the last 20 minutes. He needs to practice to manage his stamina somehow.
2)As a unit the team has quite a few moments where they were not as compact when the opposition was running at us. I think this gets better as their stamina increases. This means that when we face oppositions who are confident in their passes and their tactics there will be signs where we will get punished and this just means more drills and practices.
3)Pepe is like a lone ranger I believe he needs to utilize the overlaps of ozil & maitland niles. Think this needs to he drilled into him. The right time to go one v one or pass to teammates and use the triangle more effectively. Right now he is definitely not comfortable yet.
4)Auba if he can keep up the work rate efficiently like today in defence & attack for every game to me he is already on the way to be a legend if he stays with us. He just needs more confidence to just shoot across the goal when running into the box.
5)Sokratis overall just needs to pass from the back faster.
6)Toreirra with his commitment will get injuries we need back up for his position and in Ozils and Xhakas position as well.
7)Nelson just needs more passing accuracy practices & Saka our young blud needs confidence so more games for them.
8)Lastly Laca & Auba when Luiz has the ball they need to have an understanding to run to goal in tandem which will just unlock so much threat from nothing.

All in all the question we all have is can we have progress in every game. Some days will be bad but the match after, a response must be instilled. ❤
